data.description: You'll know that you're home as soon as you walk into this beautiful property in the desirable Bridlewood community!! Gorgeous open plan, with dual front sitting/office rooms, large dining room, spacious gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a double oven, stunning granite counter tops and cabinets, view to the living room with lots of natural light. The luxurious master suite features a master bath with soaking tub, separate tiled shower, dual sinks and walk in closet. The upstairs features SIX additional bedrooms, three of them having their own bathrooms, a bonus family room and a second story laundry room. Three car garage, two rear patios, one of them covered and complemented by a ceiling fan. Community amenities include tennis courts, a playground and community pool. This property won't last long... schedule your showing today!!
